_sText:
This is an update of my first surf map.
It's a combat surf with <font color="red">Shotguns(m3)</font>, <font color="red">MP5s</font>, <font color="red">Scouts</font> and <font color="red">AWPs</font>.
This is the final(hopefully) beta.

<fieldset><legend><font color="orange">Problems/issues:</font></legend>
Low fps from spawn. If you have any suggestions to help/fix this please tell me.
The boosts after the spawn ramp are sticky sometimes or bump you off.</fieldset>

<fieldset><legend><font color="aqua">Fixed:</font></legend>
Boosts from jail
Few small things</fieldset>

I'd greatly appreciate any suggestions or ideas for the map, as well as suggestions to fix certain problems.

Please download before rating!
Thanks!
